    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>重要提示：</strong>Color Dash 目前正在开发中，因此在演示版中，您可能会遇到一些错误或游戏问题。我们非常希望收到您的反馈，以帮助我们改进游戏！<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3260590/extras/6c989d333143bdbbbd162bcef4cbcbce.poster.avif?t=1728335164\" width=450 height=252 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3260590/extras/6c989d333143bdbbbd162bcef4cbcbce.webm?t=1728335164\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3260590/extras/6c989d333143bdbbbd162bcef4cbcbce.mp4?t=1728335164\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在 Color Dash 的演示版中，您可以在 105 个关卡中尝试 34 个关卡，这些关卡将在完整版本中提供。每个关卡都是一次充满活力的冒险，每一步都会留下印记。控制一滴油漆，克服充满致命陷阱的挑战性关卡，享受 Color Dash 演示版的氛围。节省颜料，找到安全的路径，在每个关卡中留下您独特的印记。每一个动作都很重要，每一滴颜料都弥足珍贵。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3260590/extras/b369c302386599a042195186eb93aab7.poster.avif?t=1728335164\" width=450 height=252 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3260590/extras/b369c302386599a042195186eb93aab7.webm?t=1728335164\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3260590/extras/b369c302386599a042195186eb93aab7.mp4?t=1728335164\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
